name: FIULibrariesFAQ
0:
”Alexa, ask FIU Libraries how do I print?”
”Alexa, ask FIU Libraries when the Hubert Library opens this weekend.”
”Alexa, ask FIU Libraries how to find peer-reviewed articles?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: f. i. u. libraries
des: You can ask FIU Libraries for some basic answers, like how to print, when the library closes, and how to find peer-reviewed articles. No account linking required. The FIU Librarians welcome feedback and intend to add to this skill's functionality as demand increases.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
